e mobs seem to stay some distance away.  Depends if you rest near an area of high trafic.  Here's an important tip: Sarnaks and Goblins hate each other!!!  At lev 15 I've killed some sarnark conscripts that conned red.  The trick is to watch them fight gobs that are close to the same lev.  when one of them dies attack the winner.  Usually they are close to half of there hp which makes it easier to kill them <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .  Good luck and happy hunting.<br>
Niban<br>
