<br>
I play a ranger and a mage and I will tell you straight up, this statement above will get you killed. Drachnids (spider people) CAN see thru invis. Not all of them but enough to make the trip thru &quot;spider alley&quot; a deadly risk. Assume ALL the spiders can see thru invis and avoid them if possible. You dont even need invis if you have SoW or just are smart about watching where you are going and where the spiders are at. If you want to risk it, con them while you are invis and if they are indiff to you, avoid it anyway. You never know when invis will drop. And if you are cocky enough to be near one taunting it when invis drops, you are spider poop.<br>
<br>
Other than this statement, LOIO is great for XP. Pull kitties to the lakeshore near the river intake and have a field day.<br>
